到教書<br />\n第一次經歷鬼壓床 嚇撚死"},{"pid":"79d3704b73daf31ce853babdb4d94720d06f588e","tid":1989150,"uid":91,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T17:12:53.000Z","msg":"我上次試過<br />\n大叫叫唔到郁又郁唔到之後就諗住禁開燈制<br />\n正想禁個下個腦清醒諗左諗明明我燈制琴日轉左位 點解舊個個位仲有燈制<br />\n咁我就醒左 原來係夢中夢...<br />\n<br />\n即係我發夢比鬼壓之後郁唔到出唔到聲到去想禁燈制都係發緊夢<br />\n只不過個場景係自己張床"},{"pid":"d42f65a1117a14847fc1e1b23c17d81d41a1e3f0","tid":1989150,"uid":198764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T17:13:03.000Z","msg":"我都試過好多次 初頭中學上堂瞓覺成日都會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後雖然越嚟越少 但係有埋幻聽"},{"pid":"f3fc6a7b11bfe11b7f0d3fda62f5ee799e4445a1","tid":1989150,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f15f20d6118c9842210b08d8d1907fbb7fb08ae","tid":1989150,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5da9f9fac0a7baf4b084e9b8f075826c29b837b","tid":1989150,"uid":191300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d842963e51a3012d3afefcf3ce2129fb8ddf5c5d","tid":1989150,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T17:10:25.000Z","msg":"純粹係個腦跟唔上<br />\n個腦以為你瞓咗 咁你畀嘅指令落唔到四肢<br />\n所以郁唔到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T17:11:34.000Z","msg":"郁唔到小事，幻覺幻聽先得人驚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T17:12:46.000Z","msg":"我聽到有女鬼 佢係一個女教師嘅身份喺到教書<br />\n第一次經歷鬼壓床 嚇撚死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T17:13:31.000Z","msg":"我第一次以為自己死咗tim，心唸，呢d就係死後的世界"},{"pid":"5b7129f37b2d7820eaa5f64780dce06ebdbd1235","tid":1989150,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T17:13:57.000Z","msg":"其實純粹係頸部神經麻痹"},{"pid":"ca540dce6045b175829cfedb3008bc37ab3b985f","tid":1989150,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bac290c7e74c3be5de4b23f984f49ca9489b1ea","tid":1989150,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6ae6e5160cc277c1dadc6a130a3e97f65ebfff3","tid":1989150,"uid":226020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27edbe2271eb2a1749