8726","tid":1989150,"uid":248834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T17:21:05.000Z","msg":"yes<br />\n<br />\n好記得有次撞正清明節正日<br />\n<br />\n明明日光日白，差唔多朝早訓醒既時間大約10點幾<br />\n<br />\n又係意識清醒，壓撚住唔郁得，然後好明顯感覺到張床有人係到跳！<br />\n<br />\n一定係細路仔跳果隻feel，之後好彩屋企人去完廁所，一野大力嘭門，好大聲。然後即刻郁得，即刻彈起身衝出房門係到透大氣，心跳加速，諗返仲好記得當日"},{"pid":"3609e927fde0c792a3c44b2f731de934593ac383","tid":1989150,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T17:21:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">叫佢有本事就搵黑驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n短十年命都肯"},{"pid":"1006a4efb98e7a9f19ad0b0ec34d668ca2938fa7","tid":1989150,"uid":81328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bff6e64ea2bece051eb0c15a15756a0aa3e010b","tid":1989150,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b028a62c5be4c379d349f3cdf5fcd46cbab46c7e","tid":1989150,"uid":54126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f7879d6d10e1f14aa107104d1000d482adba82a","tid":1989150,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T17:01:32.000Z","msg":"唔夠我醒，知道佢地係假的"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T17:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都識過一次<br />\n係直頭feel到佢搵張被慢慢掩我塊面想焗死我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不斷掙扎先醒得番"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T17:17:42.000Z","msg":"我試過 係夢到一隻佛地魔咁既野係咁痴埋嚟我塊面 之後我搏命嗌但嗌唔出聲 之後醒左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T17:23:07.000Z","msg":"同你有啲似<br />\n我夢到一隻男鬼係長度伸個頭<br />\n我當時面向天訓 個頭係我塊面上面<br />\n嚇醒咗 然後發現唔郁得<br />\n個心念經但係都冇用<br />\n過咗好耐好耐先郁得番 <br />\n感覺上有半個鐘但實際時間可能五分鐘都冇"},{"pid":"01648828cf7857096e34d721cd205ea54b892c08","tid":1989150,"uid"